      <title>特朗普冻结联邦土地和水域的可再生能源项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-freezes-renewable-projects-on-federal-lands-and-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在冻结在联邦土地和水域上开展风能和太阳能项目的授权，凸显出华盛顿的政策急剧转向青睐化石燃料而非可再生能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-freezes-renewable-projects-on-federal-lands-and-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
